# The song collection moved to its own dedicated git repo (2026-07-12,
# Nino's call: .tab files are the actual collection, this app's own repo
# just reads them; see ~/knowledge/projects/vinoigitare/dev-cheatsheet.md).
# Untracked here via `git rm -r --cached data/songs` -- the files
# themselves are untouched on disk, just no longer part of this repo's
# history going forward.
/data/songs/

